Package: neurons
Type: Package
Title: A Framework for Neuron Modelling, Simulation, and Analysis
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-12-20
Author: Michael Barkasi
Maintainer: Michael Barkasi <barkasi@wustl.edu>
Description: Various tools for modeling neurons. Includes functions for making growth-transform spiking networks. Defines a Cpp class 'neuron' intended to model a single neuron, accessible through R functions. Provides analysis methods for autocorrelation. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.13), RcppEigen
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen, BH, MASS
SystemRequirements: NLopt
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
